		<PackageReleaseNotes>Version 1.9.9
			- Add support for .NET 9
			- Add brush properties to TabControl
			- Added properties, events, fixes to FlatButton, MenuButton
			- Various fixes and improvements across the board
			
			Version 1.9.8
			- New SplitButton, FlatRepeatButton controls
            - Rewrote how FontSelectDialog handles font weights
            - New IClickSelectableControl interface to use with SelectPanel
            
            Version 1.9.7
			- Add TransformEditDialog, TransformEditor for PropertyList
			- Add support for .NET 8, and .NET Framework 4.0, 4.5, and 4.6.1
			- Improvements to SelectPanel, various PropertyList editors
			- Various other smaller improvements and bug fixes
            
			See website for more details!</PackageReleaseNotes>
